Value PORT (\S+)
Value NAME (.+?)
Value STATUS (up|down|disabled|notconnect)
Value VLAN (\d+|trunk)
Value DUPLEX (full|half|auto|a-full|a-half)
Value SPEED (\d+|auto)

Start
  ^---+ -> Interfaces

Interfaces
  ^${PORT}\s+${NAME}\s+${STATUS}\s+${VLAN}\s+${DUPLEX}\s+${SPEED}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^${PORT}\s+${STATUS}\s+${VLAN}\s+${DUPLEX}\s+${SPEED}\s*$$ -> Record
